---
description: Default rules for the HBI codebase
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Both main app and IQE use uv. Main app: `uv run` or source `.venv` after `uv sync --frozen` at repo root. IQE: `uv --project iqe-host-inventory-plugin ...` or source the venv in `iqe-host-inventory-plugin/.venv/` directly (see `docs/IQE.md`).
- When making changes, always test your code and make fixes as needed.
